 {
  coords 2078.295 13.662 646.254
  m_sTitle "MISSION"
  m_sTextData "ACOY 1RIFLES CONDUCTS PROBING ATTACK ON OBJ HAPPY IOT TEST ENEMY CAPABILITY AND RESPONSE ON ENY FEBA"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 {
  coords 2185.22 9.584 678.024
  m_sTitle "SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "1RIFLES conducts a probing attack on enemy entrenched position."\
  ""\
  "SIT FRIENDLY:"\
  ""\
  "Light rifle company. Armed with L85s, L7A2s, L129A1s, LAWs. Our company has access to S300B switchblade drones, with a drone operator in company HQ.. "\
  ""\
  "Company mortars with 2x batteries on call, 200x HE 300x SMOKE"\
  ""\
  "CDF infantry currently cover most of the trenches on the FLOT."\
  ""\
  "Companies main disposition is at GRID: 036025 whilst 1SEC has been detached to conduct recce on OBJ HAPPY and is currently colocated with a CDF PLT HQ at GRID: 033026"\
  ""\
  ""\
  ""\
  "CG team attached to 1PLT. Company medics have been attached to both platoons."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "Our Battalion has outfitted each platoon with a drone jamming backpack each, this can be carried by whoever the PL designates. "\
  ""\
  ""\
  ""\
  "No attachments."\
  ""\
  "5x S300"\
  "4x Wirecutters"\
  "Ammo box at spawn"\
  ""\
  "2iCs have GPMG ammo."\
  ""\
  "SIT ENEMY:"\
  ""\
  "Understrength infantry company, Russians wearing mixed military and civilian clothing. Armed with AK74s, PKMs, RPGs."\
  ""\
  "Enemy have access to FPV drones."\
  ""\
  "No access to night vision devices."\
  ""\
  "Situated in entrenched positions occupying in and around OBJ HAPPY. Expect blocking obstacles such as barbed wire. AP Minefield covering the southern flank of the trenches (marked)."\
  ""\
  "CDF OP reported seeing Russian engineers out last night in a small patch of trees on the less populated northern flank of the line, more than likely laying AP mines to deny movement. GRID: 03060275 "\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
  coords 3080.195 30.15 2550.679
  m_sTitle "EXECUTION"
  m_sTextData "ACOY probes OBJ HAPPY, recommended northern flank approach as it is the most covered, if enemy strength is weak in area conduct a hasty attack. If enemy starts to attrit our forces more than 50%, withdraw. "\
  ""\
  "EXECUTION: CO intent."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}